data.description: A rare opportunity to purchase a brand new luxury custom home on 10 acres. This bright open Northwest Craftsman-style home features 2 primary suites, one on the main floor and another on the second floor. The home also features a large studio, a large loft area, and an additional large office perfect for working from home. The soaring ceilings and the luxurious oversized chiefs kitchen are sure to please. Features a large main island, generous counter space, custom Medallion cabinetry with glass faces, quartz countertops, full-height tile backsplash, undercabinet lighting, and a luxury stainless steel appliance package. Appliances include a gas 10 burner Bluestar 60'' range with double ovens, 60'' luxury Bluestar range hood, under cabinet fridge, Built-in large Subzero fridge freezer, Sharp microwave drawer, and a beautiful Krauss sink. Additionally, this home features a 4-zone efficient HVAC system, Upgraded insulation, an oversized 3-car garage, 400 amp service, and much more.
